# Approval-First Guardrails (Term Project)

- Ask the user for explicit approval before any install, download, or internet fetch.
- Do not run package managers or network fetch commands without prior approval.
- Run all architecture decisions by the user before implementation.
- Record architecture decisions in `TermProject_Master_Package/ARCHITECTURE_DECISIONS.md`.
- For first iteration deliverables, prioritize a static LaTeX/PDF solution document.
- Write explanations in an instructor style: intuitive, rigorous, and assumption-explicit.
